Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.view.GUI

Interface PaymentController

All Known Implementing Classes:
ActivateProductionController, BuyDevCardController
public interface PaymentController
Interface that allows to handle player's decision while performing an action that requires picking resources from warehouse.

    • editedCostList

      default boolean editedCostList​(java.util.List<Pair<ResourceType,​java.lang.Integer>> neededResources, int resourceIndex, int taken, int currentValue, javafx.scene.control.TextField resource)
      Method that modifies its first parameter according to player's selection.
      Parameters:
      neededResources - list possibly edited.
      resourceIndex - index of list element.
      taken - number of resources taken.
      currentValue - occurrences of needed resource type.
      resource - text field that displays current value of occurrences selected.
      Returns:
      true if the list corresponding to the first parameter of the method has been edited.

    • addToCostList

      default boolean addToCostList​(java.util.List<Pair<ResourceType,​java.lang.Integer>> neededResources, int resourceIndex, int taken, int currentValue, javafx.scene.control.TextField resource)
      Method that adds some occurrences related to a certain resource type in list given as the first parameter after that a player has clicked on a minus button.
      Parameters:
      neededResources - list to edit.
      resourceIndex - index of resource type related to selection.
      taken - number of occurrences subtracted to current value.
      currentValue - number of occurrences currently selected.
      resource - text field that displays current value of occurrences selected.
      Returns:
      true if some occurrences have been added to the costs list.
